All Screenshots are available in the respective projecy folder

9. Learning Outcomes:

- Understanding of Spring Boot and Maven project setup
- Knowledge of JPA and entity relationships
- API design principles for RESTful services
- Practical experience with H2 in-memory database
- Documentation with Swagger UI